OL,3,CGraeme Souness to swim Channel twice
OL,4,Cto fund research into Epidermolysis
OL,5,CBullosa
OL,7,FLiverpool legend Graeme Souness is
OL,8,Ftaking on another huge fundraising
OL,9,Fswim, to raise money for research into
OL,10,Ftreatments of the rare skin condition
OL,11,FEpidermolysis Bullosa (EB).
OL,13,FThe former player and manager, famed
OL,14,Ffor his toughness, was once again
OL,15,Fmoved to tears during an interview
OL,16,Fwith ITV News while talking about the
OL,17,Fcondition, and how it's affecting his
OL,18,Ffriend Isla Grist, who lives with EB.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
