OL,5,CBullosa
OL,7,FIn May, Graeme will join five others
OL,8,Fin a relay swim from Dover to Calais,
OL,9,Fand back again.
OL,11,FIt follows similar fundraising drives
OL,12,Fin 2023 and 2024. The 71-year-old
OL,13,Fhopes to raise more than #750,000 to
OL,14,Ffund research into treatments for the
OL,15,Fcondition, and to raise awareness.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
