OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Granada presenter
OL,8,FGamal Fahnbulleh on Wednesday, he
OL,9,Fsaid: "I came across this horrible,
OL,10,Fhorrendous disease six years ago, and
OL,11,Fit was like someone punched me on the
OL,12,Fnose. I now have the time to dedicate
OL,13,Fto it."
OL,15,FMuch of that time is dedicated to
OL,16,Fsupporting Isla Grist, a sixteen-year-
OL,17,Fold from Scotland who lives with the
OL,18,Fcondition and campaigns for more
OL,19,Fawareness of those who live with it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
