OL,4,Cto fund research into Epidermolysis
OL,5,CBullosa
OL,7,FThrough their work together, their
OL,8,Ffriendship has blossomed.
OL,10,FIsla told ITV News: "It is a great
OL,11,Fprivilege to know this old softy, but
OL,12,Fit's one of the few relationships that
OL,13,Fcome along and stay for the long haul."
OL,15,FDescribing the realities of living
OL,16,Fwith EB, she said: "EB is such a
OL,17,Ffrustrating condition that is just so
OL,18,Fhard to do anything with, you're
OL,19,Falways in pain, even just sitting and
OL,20,Ftalking, there's some aspect of pain
OL,21,Fand discomfort."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
