OL,3,CGraeme Souness to swim Channel twice
OL,4,Cto fund research into Epidermolysis
OL,5,CBullosa
OL,7,F"Dressing changes can take up to five
OL,8,Fhours, you're cold, sore, exhausted
OL,9,Fand all you want to do is go to bed.
OL,10,FIt's so extremely painful that I'm on
OL,11,Fsome of the heaviest drugs you can
OL,12,Fimagine, to get me through that five
OL,13,Fhour period."
OL,15,F"It's so hard and so mentally
OL,16,Fchallenging as well as physically, it
OL,17,Freally does put into perspective how
OL,18,Feasy some things are for other people,
OL,19,Fand it's not like that for everyone."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
