OL,5,CBullosa
OL,7,FIsla, who's from Inverness, has
OL,8,Fendured more than 80 operations to
OL,9,Fdeal with the condition.
OL,11,FAddressing her strength, Graeme said:
OL,12,F"Football is all about people who can
OL,13,Fdig in when the going gets tough,
OL,14,Fbeing a winner. This is on a
OL,15,Fcompletely different level. Isla has
OL,16,Fpainted a picture for you how
OL,17,Fdifficult like is. It's actually a lot
OL,18,Fworse than that."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
