OL,3,CGraeme Souness to swim Channel twice
OL,4,Cto fund research into Epidermolysis
OL,5,CBullosa
OL,7,F"I've seen Isla's skin and it's as if
OL,8,Fsomeone has taken a blowtorch to her
OL,9,Fskin, and that's not an exaggeration,
OL,10,Fit's constantly weeping and constantly
OL,11,Fred raw."
OL,13,F"Isla is an absolute trojan, she
OL,14,Freally is the real deal, if you want a
OL,15,Ftough cookie. Everything is groundhog
OL,16,Fday for her."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
