OL,3,CGraeme Souness to swim Channel twice
OL,4,Cto fund research into Epidermolysis
OL,5,CBullosa
OL,7,FThe pair's previous challenges have
OL,8,Fseen them raise more than 1.5 million
OL,9,Ffor the Debra UK Charity, which
OL,10,Fenabled them to commission the first
OL,11,Ftwo EB clinical trials.
OL,13,FGraeme said: "There's 20 drugs we want
OL,14,Fto try and make useful. That's going
OL,15,Fto cost the best part of ten million.
OL,16,FIf we discovered a drug today it might
OL,17,Fbe ten to fifteen years before it got
OL,18,Fto the market. We're trying to
OL,19,Fshortcut this, by repurposing drugs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
