OL,4,Cto fund research into Epidermolysis
OL,5,CBullosa
OL,7,FBecoming emotional, he continued:
OL,8,F"Ten, fifteen years time, isn't going
OL,9,Fto help Isla and the kids living with
OL,10,Fthis today, it's now."
OL,12,FWhile the cure for the condition may
OL,13,Fbe a long way off, any sort of relief
OL,14,Fis welcomed by Isla.
OL,16,FShe said: "It would be amazing to find
OL,17,Fsome relief, but even just small
OL,18,Fthings can make a huge difference. A
OL,19,Flittle bit less itch, a little bit
OL,20,Fless pain, a little bit more sleep,
OL,21,Fanything would help."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
